{"type":"article_comment","id":228517,"parentType":"article","parentId":13800,"uid":15243,"contents":"<blockquote>平野耕太表示这锅我不背 </blockquote><br>\n那个真是太好笑了，充分说明了粉蛆不仅素质差，识汉字的水平也大有问题：<br>\n<br>\n来自中国的人，对《我的英雄学院》不满为啥找我抱怨？倒是确认一下名字啊，我叫平野耕太，英雄学院是堀越耕平，就对上两个汉字而已。<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cb1d95862627b2ce887c5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cb1d95862627b2ce887c5.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cb1d95862627b2ce887c5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d425afe373078c9a2a12b.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d425afe373078c9a2a12b.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d425afe373078c9a2a12b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-05","agreeCount":28,"discussionCount":0}